    ⟨⟨source⟩,
      presieveFreeSemanticAtomLawInputBoundarySource_constructs_presieveSectionExtensionAndOverlapLaw
        skeleton source,
      source.exposes_pointwise_nonvacuity_support_and_presieve_evaluation⟩

